    "https://leetcode.com/problems/frequency-of-the-most-frequent-element?envType=company&amp;envId=google&amp;favoriteSlug=google-three-months": "Sort in ascending order\nUse sliding window l, r = 0, 0\n\n- Rightmost value is the target\n- Valid: nums[r] * (r - l + 1) - total < k\n\n- Keep the sum of the current window\n- Check if the cost exceeds k\n- Shrink until the window becomes affordable\n- The largest valid window is the answer.",
